#3DPrintingNerd #3DPrinting #3DPrinter

3D Printing Nerd is a channel devoted to the wonderful world of 3d printing. We like to cover all things from hobby and consumer level, all the way up to the industrial additive manufacturing machines and businesses. We talk to people and find the story, and then through conversation let those people tell you their story
